### ==========================================
### 💰 BID ENDPOINTS
### ==========================================

### Submit Bid (Freelancer only — login as freelancer first)
POST http://localhost:6868/api/bid
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "projectId": "PROJECT_ID_HERE",
    "proposedPrice": 3500,
    "deliveryDays": 7,
    "coverNote": "I have 2 years of React experience and have built 5+ portfolio sites. I can deliver a pixel-perfect responsive design with smooth animations."
}

###

### Submit Bid — Second Freelancer (login as sara@test.com first)
POST http://localhost:6868/api/bid
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "projectId": "PROJECT_ID_HERE",
    "proposedPrice": 4000,
    "deliveryDays": 5,
    "coverNote": "Full-stack developer specializing in modern React apps. I'll include free revisions and source code documentation."
}

###

### Get All Bids for a Project
GET http://localhost:6868/api/bid/project/PROJECT_ID_HERE

###

### Get My Bids (Freelancer only — paginated)
GET http://localhost:6868/api/bid/my?page=1&limit=10

###

### Get My Bids — filter by status
GET http://localhost:6868/api/bid/my?status=PENDING

###

### Edit Bid (Freelancer owner, while PENDING)
PUT http://localhost:6868/api/bid/BID_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "proposedPrice": 3000,
    "deliveryDays": 6,
    "coverNote": "Updated: I can deliver in 6 days at a reduced price."
}

###

### Withdraw Bid (Freelancer owner)
DELETE http://localhost:6868/api/bid/BID_ID_HERE

###

### Accept Bid (Client who owns the project)
PUT http://localhost:6868/api/bid/BID_ID_HERE/accept

###

### Reject Bid (Client who owns the project)
PUT http://localhost:6868/api/bid/BID_ID_HERE/reject

###
